{"tid":1116432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎棟國：一地兩檢至今未有公安「佐敦道拉人」","createTime":"2019-04-20T03:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T10:54:00.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d99dbdb261739f3a55bacb0dd422bb534c6e3fae","tid":1116432,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T03:51:16.000Z","msg":"同樣曾任保安局長的新民黨主席葉劉淑儀和該黨常務副主席黎棟國，今早到商台節目回應《逃犯條例》修訂。身兼行會成員的葉劉淑儀認為，政府的確「推得急了一點」，欠正式諮詢，但她指相關內容並非新事物，她任保安局長時，已多次到立法會解釋相關國際慣例和背景等，現在「政府才當是延續過去工作提出來」。<br />\n<br />\n對有意見憂慮內地濫用條例，令港人被移交到內地受審，黎棟國批評是極度誇大和不符實際情況。他以高鐵西九龍站一地兩檢為例，稱開通至今也無內地公安在「佐敦道拉人」，或在高鐵西九龍站「暗門扯人」，強調今次修例是有長久歷史和依照國際水平，而非香港獨創。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀稱，中英聯合聯絡小組在香港回歸前因需討論大量議題，「在當時時空的限制下，只可商討至中方同意本地立法，通過移交逃犯、刑事司法互助、移交判刑人士的法例本地化，當時港英政府無地位與北京討論」，強調有關工作需交特區政府處理。<br />\n<br />\n她又表示，疑犯可申請人身保護令，並用多種理由抗辯，加上移交程序複雜和冗長，訟費也由申請方支付，「（內地）如果要追究你，你一踏足西九龍內地管轄區便可追究，透過香港法院做是很麻煩」。對港人不信任內地法律制度，葉劉淑儀說，香港法庭有多年處理個案的經驗，港人不應「自製恐懼」。<br />\n<br />\n對有人質疑香港特首和律政司檢視中央提出個案的標準，會不同於來自其他司法管轄區的個案，黎棟國認為說法不公道。他表示，律政司對本港法治是很重要的「守護者」，加上社會知悉律政司決定，過程具透明度，市民亦可對特首決定提司法覆核。"},{"pid":"7cfe891474f9dbc94d18ca2af3a79220a4b4c767","tid":1116432,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T03:51:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190420/s00001/1555728833481/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190420%2Fs00001%2F1555728833481%2F&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLPY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=f2cbabd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190420%2Fs00001%2F1555728833481%2F&h=d588e474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190420/s00001/1555728833481/</a>"},{"pid":"7050fed8f6b39d28f527dfa111a211dd159a9fc4","tid":1116432,"uid":20815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"如果有咁點？"},{"pid":"39c818c2a5abf2336b8293913e21b95625840eed","tid":1116432,"uid":997,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"李波果壇野都未撚搞掂,屌你老母"},{"pid":"ebda4ce4e6c921ac9a4074ed4ab0fc7f95a6df67","tid":1116432,"uid":165136,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T03:57:47.000Z","msg":"無就唔好特別講啦屌<br />\n定係只係佐敦道無其他地方有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b58836601ea946d420f02b470bbecb82651e4b9","tid":1116432,"uid":90704,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:01:10.000Z","msg":"佐敦道安全，彌敦道先拉"},{"pid":"3bf34148dc85ffa54486b863b5eb9586fae4a228","tid":1116432,"uid":166474,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:03:21.000Z","msg":"拉撚左你都唔知啦，洗唔洗開埋記者會公佈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a936e2900624b5398d310778ee5e071265030622","tid":1116432,"uid":50386,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:04:04.000Z","msg":"偷換概念<br />\n<br />\n一地兩檢公安響佐敦道拉人係跨境執法，<br />\n做咗都唔比得人知<br />\n<br />\n送中條例通過嘅話就隨時砌條罪就可以引渡，<br />\n比晒全香港人知都唔驚你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd23edca6791dabf3f8b38f483a06665a6e69b4c","tid":1116432,"uid":33907,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:04:29.000Z","msg":"要坐艇 係海邊先拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d700215f4a73d48b39ae4a3e40c523cd4e08e536","tid":1116432,"uid":188282,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:05:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">或在高鐵西九龍站暗門扯人</span><br />\n<br />\n做左市民都唔知啦。"},{"pid":"46c3e6f0fa9e3bf5ce7189f8cb1a9d83fe6f8935","tid":1116432,"uid":133695,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:06:57.000Z","msg":"講到好似合理咁 本身就唔合理 仲係度吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489e4e3e70a667691f0743dedde8604a50420c3d","tid":1116432,"uid":42804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7050fed8f6b39d28f527dfa111a211dd159a9fc4","tid":1116432,"uid":20815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"如果有咁點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:21:40.000Z","msg":"個別事件，不作評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即使最終變成一個月幾次，到時改口話中國公安有權在港執行職務，更何況就算真係公然捉香港人又如何？中國公安唔通會著住制服做野明目張膽？"},{"pid":"378c587e0955d43286052c15c9cb683bf9cd77a3","tid":1116432,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b58836601ea946d420f02b470bbecb82651e4b9","tid":1116432,"uid":90704,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:01:10.000Z","msg":"佐敦道安全，彌敦道先拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:36:27.000Z","msg":"解放軍冇喺天安門殺人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282792c4a008740ba1709557402b4d14076124e2","tid":1116432,"uid":185022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7050fed8f6b39d28f527dfa111a211dd159a9fc4","tid":1116432,"uid":20815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"如果有咁點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"唔評論個別事件<br />\n相信內地政府嘅法治"},{"pid":"c90364f6aba71d1461437a216f0e935a8183daab","tid":1116432,"uid":157369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"但係有送中條例就可以由香港警察喺佐敦道拉你，暗門都唔使，大搖大擺喺西九龍條黃線移送你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7261f06fcba6340ca062df9a4bf0078c8dd8809","tid":1116432,"uid":140831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:39:33.000Z","msg":"多謝黎生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港果然係最安全既地方"},{"pid":"672a21e3a6477356ccdca4007cc8bd0c092c0e5e","tid":1116432,"uid":133806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:40:21.000Z","msg":"咁柯士甸道呢？"},{"pid":"73d34c8cf9e825f97764697bd63b58eaf8d23eae","tid":1116432,"uid":8478,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T05:00:35.000Z","msg":"內地《南方都市報》今日報道，深圳龍崗法院上月中派員到西九龍高鐵站，帶走一名「被執行人」回深圳調查，這宗個案原來並非去年9月高鐵香港段通車後第一宗同類事件。翻查資料，內地媒體去年10月報道，一名龍姓香港永久性居民，據報因房屋買賣合同糾紛，於西九龍高鐵站內地口岸區被拘留。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：【一地兩檢】深圳法院派員西九高鐵站拉人<br />\n<br />\n跟《南方都市報》同屬南方報業的新媒體《南方+客戶端》去年10月31日報道，龍某在2015年因房屋買賣合同糾紛，與買方在南山法院對簿公堂；法院判龍某須歸還訂金100萬元人民幣。由於龍某其後未有履行判決，法院遂通報全國口岸，希望相關部門協助。<br />\n<br />\n去年10月27日，南山法院接獲香港西九站內地口岸區邊檢部門電話，稱已扣留龍某；同日晚上法院職員抵達西九站，與邊檢部門完成交接手續。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，龍某被帶至法院後，已要求親屬一次性支付相關款項，及後法官決定提前解除拘留措施。<br />\n<br />\n明拉明搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a50236dcf996b8b2864601e95c912ad7eb3452","tid":1116432,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"有嗰陣咪又係個別事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f468df681645f978134af2bccd636ff57a364423","tid":1116432,"uid":66810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T05:50:39.000Z","msg":"拉完話你知咩"},{"pid":"0511dd5ac5d748abc8dbcab63ec4a63613e33d3a","tid":1116432,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"因為係銅鑼灣拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c99212e73eecdcd486dc4a7a40d3f4bd7d09fcf","tid":1116432,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:04:10.000Z","msg":"即係公安可以喺佐敦道拉人,只係未有案例"},{"pid":"ad279d86f848dc9aaadc9822bb2b84902cc8037f","tid":1116432,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:08:12.000Z","msg":"只會係佐敦道以外拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3109e36de96cf85c8f664b1d0bed9c01e2f8a1","tid":1116432,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:08:45.000Z","msg":"因為好快有有逃犯條例,冇必要偷偷地拉人了,反正走唔出香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e638c02ffb74329f29e5b6cc5f611bf03493d17d","tid":1116432,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T09:56:06.000Z","msg":"未"}]}